## Importmap Usage

### Importing Modules

```javascript
// app/javascript/application.js

// Import Stimulus
import '@hotwired/turbo-rails'
import './controllers'

// Import external libraries (via Importmap)
import { Chart } from 'chart.js'

// Use imported library
const chart = new Chart(ctx, config)
```

### Adding Packages to Importmap

```bash
# Add package via importmap
bin/importmap pin chart.js

# Pin specific version
bin/importmap pin lodash@4.17.21

# Unpin package
bin/importmap unpin chart.js
```

